# HTML Report Output

- Save all generated HTML reports inside the workspace-level `Reports` folder by default.
- The report directory is `C:\Users\user\Documents\Cursor\Reports`.
- Do not default HTML reports to data-specific folders such as `Data/SportsAPI/Reports`.
- Keep source scripts outside `Reports`; only generated report artifacts should go there.
